#define USER_DATA_EMPTY   0
 

List of RTAI FIFO device file numbers called "/dev/rtf#" (where # represents the file number). USER-DATA empty buffer FIFO (external).

FIFOs may be calssified as either internal or external. Those that communicate between USER space and the RTAI SDSU driver are considered to be external where as all others are internally used by the RTAI SDSU driver.
